from jmd jim de arra subject re my gun be like my american expres card in article thoma parsli thomasp write observation from a naive norwegian gun be make to kill person not to shoot target or to have something more macho than stamp to collect it is more easy to someone with a gun than with a knife or a bat a in baseball it not very wise to compare two completely different country like usa and let say island on issue like crime and violence ye the problem be person commit crime not the tool beeing use but should be take into concideration only a far a it affect the crime rate we have a very strict gun-legislation in norway but until recently it wa possible for enyone over year to buy a shotgun shotgun be use mainly for hunt in norway but because it wa so easy to accuire one it wa the most use gun in crime the solution wa to restrict the sale so it now necessary to apply and register ymy shotgun and unbelievable the use of gun in crime fell did the rate of crime fall if not the ban wa of no use it be the rate of violent crime that matter not the tool use it the crime stupid there be now a new law against wear long knife in public and why should it be allow apparently that become the weapon of choice after the shotgun be ban after that they decide the car of choice be the saab and propose a ban on that what i a an scandinavian have problem to understand be that you american have a more liberal view on gun and violence than on nudity and sex try show a bare breast on tv insted of violence and murder ye i know a little american history but be it a right to have an assault gun in ymy home an handgun in ymy car ye we still trust honest person here for the time be the bad english be not my fault it probably the keyboard-software or the quality of the subtext on tv disclamer not these be the view of all studen at my university all norwegian and probably whole of the universe thoma parsli thomasp jmd i alway rethink that there never be a day when i have rethink that but i c